Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁断皇帝 阿图尔·贾兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其女儿将是他的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是肩负命运之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的存在 仅仅是个开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方等待的是超乎人们想象的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 不过是件推动命运的工具罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背着棺材的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能干脆哪里掉着钱吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我拿你下锅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这深山里搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭…袭击?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁袭击? 袭击谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫…劫路贼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉你又猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正处于无业中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没吃的东西果腹 所以跑来挖野菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穷人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领会 无业穷人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没说错但令人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你又在这种地方干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西是棺材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山 无人 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 这个 假装没看到 没见过 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那棺材里装了实物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…你是个杀人犯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人 不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅人! 柔弱的旅人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地 戴尔索兰特市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无比遥远…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这山里走多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般哪用走那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明显迷路了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震惊的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上有钱不?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷! 穷人! 劫路贼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是想你请我吃早饭我替你带路啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以神不知鬼不觉地将你带进城里去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然看你这样子 一辈子也别想走下山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Moruzerun Moruzerun Emurun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独角马…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…倒霉透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这玩意儿丢掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝 接触不得 贵重品!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥? 什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 没办法 我收回前言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那棺材可千万别放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}Moruzerun Moruzerun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被它吃掉 就给我抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 肚子饿得使不出力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然 强硬 乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包扎 紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是独角马 它不用多久还会袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 包扎 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对甩不掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 无趣的一生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡 不畏惧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说真一点不怕 那是瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我活着也没什么可干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样的世界里 我就是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机杖?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你是魔法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物 同样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 只会这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他 废物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这个 能办到 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 干掉独角马?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法术式 起动中 移动 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延时间就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要争取到时间 你就能用魔法了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为钢也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢故不怯 钢故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敌 尽无一切踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为灭此凶器也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 驽马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kokult elum Naikt inte Naint kum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ee wam ee wam milta ru Kokult elum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naikt inte naint
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告战终
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为人也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存! 两人 生存!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 很强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行啦 毕竟曾经是乱破师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是废物 发挥了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏 有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 算是尽了份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新委托 带路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字 你?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 托鲁·亚裘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·贾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·托勒庞特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能更好地使驭你 你也不至于葬身于此了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟打败了弃兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么人物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩儿应一直是独自行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了协助者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊愕的胃袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动完肚子会特别饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且呀 能吃的时候不多吃点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你钱够吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而野菜 又在哪儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为你终于肯干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到没去挖野菜 而是摘了个少女回来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还和个如此水灵的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸对脸 在这儿坐着吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺潇洒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你整天整天也不去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在家里无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠我一个人维持家计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这男的真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 等等 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你误会了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我误会了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子愚钝 还请开示一二吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 「不称职的老哥」这个评价是跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把等候早餐的妹妹忘在脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光顾着自己大吃大喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还砸了我的店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且无论饭钱还是赔款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都丢给刚认识的这女孩付账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊得我连气都生不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你身上闻到浓浓的废柴味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了弃兽的袭击?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话 我真能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 然后得这丫头帮助 干掉了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材里放着机杖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这伤就是战斗的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后请客吃饭 就是带路的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 委托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 乱破师兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可我都多少年没工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然要我干活…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去工作 还是被我制成标本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请选一条路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这两条?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 兄长你希望由我亲手制成标本?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不得不工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎莅临寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是罗伯特·阿巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是叫…亚伯力克·基烈特是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您年轻得令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本听闻来的是克里曼机关的人 我还以为定是位老者呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到基烈特家 那可是大大的名门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要从事这份工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下对自己现在日夜为其奔走的工作感到自豪和责任感 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉我问了个失礼的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了请问 此次造访所为何事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下很清楚我们初次见面此举显得十分唐突无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一事不得不相求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听闻您乃讨伐贾兹皇帝的八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想请您将在贾兹帝国帝都攻防战一役中得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「战利品」交予在下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我将战利品 返还?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 为何需要它?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下由于事需保密 不能告知您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴尔特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的心情我十分理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 此问题不仅关系到维马克王国
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至攸关整个菲尔毕斯特大陆的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今要我返还?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 不花时间 简单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领主 阿巴尔特伯爵府邸 袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 我 就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑子没事儿吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常 需要 无论如何都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要做的事情 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要做的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做 义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗费一生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若要袭击 那还得做很多准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说伯爵出身武门世家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天实际见面 我感到有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起来实在不像一位精通武艺之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战后五年 武艺生疏了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那宅子 也透着一丝古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何处古怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫兵的数量少得出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以领主府邸来说 警备显得太松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺令人在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕也是因为知道阿巴尔特伯爵是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才来到这个城市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 得到了协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会动袭击伯爵府邸的念头…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去监视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是要偷什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想说 我们也没必要追问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做好自己工作就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「工作」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从兄长你口中听到 真是有种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 房子西面的情况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和东面同样的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟要和领主动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长你怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁怕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 兄长自然是浑身是胆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便手无寸铁一丝不挂赤身裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也定能勇敢无畏笑迎千军万马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那从各种意义上来说 都只是个傻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是兄长你本人 也绝不允许侮辱我敬爱的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 傻子应该是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就好」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想潜进去好像不是很难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说宅子的主人是在那贾兹帝都攻防战中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为先锋冲进城堡的勇士之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那想必是个不折不扣的武斗派啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得借助她的魔法力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这个 那丫头 真的可以信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是委托人啊 还谈什么信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我指的是她作为魔法师的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那可是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰呀起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Burner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面包 大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫兵少得有点在意 不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照商量好的行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面放着机杖是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携入 必然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为钢也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢故不怯 钢故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敌 尽无一切踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为灭此凶器也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 和托鲁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 再用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待遇 不正当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下来怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要偷什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本能明白 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是要你让我们也明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上 就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显现吧 探测者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的东西 宅邸中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发 青白光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们分两头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责一楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你和她负责二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克里曼机关的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来对白天的铩羽而归 很是不满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正为难得的宝物无处使用 而感觉稍许无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…魔法师?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可和你们上司那骑士小少爷不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来 这家伙是个魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该已经死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途 终要起程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 会认真工作? 一丝不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 稍稍怪人 同样不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 遗体收集 还请声援!
